{"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"notebook":"React-web","section":"React Hooks","page":{"id":"0-28592de22ebf3a4f8a305bb46b9e53a8!1-BC575AB8E2AB9833!2238","self":"https://www.onenote.com/api/v1.0/me/notes/pages/0-28592de22ebf3a4f8a305bb46b9e53a8!1-BC575AB8E2AB9833!2238","createdTime":"2019-03-01T13:24:45.663Z","title":"State Hook: useState","createdByAppId":"","links":{"oneNoteEmbedUrl":{"href":"https://onedrive.live.com/redir.aspx?cid=bc575ab8e2ab9833&page=edit&resid=BC575AB8E2AB9833!2142&parId=BC575AB8E2AB9833!109&wd=target%28React%20Hooks.one%7C27c2f887-9a0a-ed42-9303-4603415b556d%2FState%20Hook%20useState%7C9b707e22-9c46-6b44-924b-8c23b893fdd6%2F%29"},"oneNoteClientUrl":{"href":"onenote:https://d.docs.live.net/bc575ab8e2ab9833/Documents/React-web/React%20Hooks.one#State%20Hook%20useState&section-id=27c2f887-9a0a-ed42-9303-4603415b556d&page-id=9b707e22-9c46-6b44-924b-8c23b893fdd6&end"},"oneNoteWebUrl":{"href":"https://onedrive.live.com/redir.aspx?cid=bc575ab8e2ab9833&page=edit&resid=BC575AB8E2AB9833!2142&parId=BC575AB8E2AB9833!109&wd=target%28React%20Hooks.one%7C27c2f887-9a0a-ed42-9303-4603415b556d%2FState%20Hook%20useState%7C9b707e22-9c46-6b44-924b-8c23b893fdd6%2F%29"}},"contentUrl":"https://www.onenote.com/api/v1.0/me/notes/pages/0-28592de22ebf3a4f8a305bb46b9e53a8!1-BC575AB8E2AB9833!2238/content","lastModifiedTime":"2019-04-10T02:57:25Z","parentSection@odata.context":"https://www.onenote.com/api/v1.0/$metadata#me/notes/sections('0-BC575AB8E2AB9833%212238')/pages('0-28592de22ebf3a4f8a305bb46b9e53a8%211-BC575AB8E2AB9833%212238')/parentSection(id,name,self)/$entity","parentSection":{"id":"0-BC575AB8E2AB9833!2238","name":"React Hooks","self":"https://www.onenote.com/api/v1.0/me/notes/sections/0-BC575AB8E2AB9833!2238"},"content":"       useState의 쓰임               import React, { useState } from 'react';￼￼function Example() {￼  const [ count, setCount ] = useState(0);￼}                      count와 setCount변수에 주목한다.     count는 this.state.count와 동일한 것이고,     setCount는 아래와 동일한 기능을 한다고 보면 된다.                  function(arg) {         this.setState({ count: arg })       }                       useState의 파라미터값은 initial state라고 불리우는데, 해당 예제에 맞춰 설명을 하자면 setCount({설정할 state값}) 이나 마찬가지다. 즉, 초기화 할 state값이 인자로 들어가게 된다.            useState는 Array destructuring방식을 채택한다.     Reactjs.org- Tip: What Do Square Brackets Mean?    변수명을 사용자 마음대로 지정할 수 있게 하기 위함이라고 한다.    Destructuring하지 않는 스타일로는 아래의 코드와 같다.                 var fruitStateVariable = useState('banana'); // Returns a pair￼  var fruit = fruitStateVariable[0]; // First item in a pair￼  var setFruit = fruitStateVariable[1]; // Second item in a pair                 기존 state를 이용하여 업데이트하려면, Functional update    Reactjs.org - Functional updates    보통 state를 update하는 함수의 인자에는 변경하고자 하는 state값을 넣는 방법도 있지만, 기존의 state값을 기억하지 않고 그냥 뒤집어 쓰는 형태가 된다.    그래서 기존의 state값 + 추가&변경하고자 하는 state값 적용을 하고 싶다면, update함수의 인자에다가 함수를 넣어주면 된다.               function Counter({initialCount}) {        const [count, setCount] = useState(initialCount);        return (          <>            Count: {count}            <button onClick={() => setCount(initialCount)}>Reset</button>            <button onClick={() => setCount(prevCount => prevCount + 1)}>+</button>            <button onClick={() => setCount(prevCount => prevCount - 1)}>-</button>          </>        );      }                       초기화 state를 Lazy하게 쓰기    Reactjs.org - Lazy initial state    초기화 state(initialState)를 하려는 값이 복잡하고 많은 연산이 필요한 비싼 로직을 거쳐야 한다면 고려해야 할 방법이라고 한다.        쓰는 방법은 useState함수의 인자에다가 값 대신 함수를 넣어준다.               const [state, setState] = useState(() => {        const initialState = someExpensiveComputation(props);        return initialState;      });                   사실 문서만을 읽어서는 어떨 때에 쓰는 지 와닿지가 않아서 좀 더 스터디가 필요해 보인다..       ","html":"\n\t\t<div style=\"position:absolute;left:67px;top:119px;width:557px\">\n\t\t\t<h2 style=\"font-size:14pt;color:#2e75b5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">useState<span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC758;</span> <span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC4F0;&#xC784;</span></h2>\n\t\t\t<table style=\"border:1px solid;border-collapse:collapse\">\n\t\t\t\t<tbody><tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color:black;border:1px solid\"><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding;color:white\">import React, { </span><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding;color:yellow\">useState</span><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding;color:white\"> } from &apos;react&apos;;</span><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding;color:white\">&#xFFFC;</span><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding;color:white\">&#xFFFC;</span><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding;color:white\">function Example() {</span><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding;color:white\">&#xFFFC;</span><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding;color:white\">  </span><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding;color:yellow\">const [ count, setCount ] = useState(0);</span><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding;color:white\">&#xFFFC;</span><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding;color:white\">}</span></td>\n\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t</tbody></table>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li><span style=\"font-weight:bold\">count</span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC640;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic;font-weight:bold\">setCount</span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xBCC0;&#xC218;&#xC5D0;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC8FC;&#xBAA9;&#xD55C;&#xB2E4;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">.</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic;font-weight:bold\">count</span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xB294;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic;font-weight:bold\">this.state.count</span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC640;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xB3D9;&#xC77C;&#xD55C;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xAC83;&#xC774;&#xACE0;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">,</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic;font-weight:bold\">setCount</span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xB294;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC544;&#xB798;&#xC640;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xB3D9;&#xC77C;&#xD55C;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xAE30;&#xB2A5;&#xC744;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xD55C;&#xB2E4;&#xACE0;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xBCF4;&#xBA74;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xB41C;&#xB2E4;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">.</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<table style=\"border:1px solid;border-collapse:collapse\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<tbody><tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color:black;border:1px solid\"><p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding;color:white\">function(arg) {</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding;color:white\">  </span><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding;color:yellow\">this.setState({ count: arg })</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding;color:white\">}</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t</tbody></table>\n\t\t\t\t<li><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic;font-weight:bold\">useState</span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC758;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xD30C;&#xB77C;&#xBBF8;&#xD130;&#xAC12;&#xC740;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic;text-decoration:underline\">initial state</span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xB77C;&#xACE0;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xBD88;&#xB9AC;&#xC6B0;&#xB294;&#xB370;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">, </span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xD574;&#xB2F9;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC608;&#xC81C;&#xC5D0;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xB9DE;&#xCDB0;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC124;&#xBA85;&#xC744;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xD558;&#xC790;&#xBA74;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic;font-weight:bold\">setCount({</span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic;font-weight:bold\">&#xC124;&#xC815;&#xD560;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic;font-weight:bold\"> state</span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic;font-weight:bold\">&#xAC12;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic;font-weight:bold\">}) </span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC774;&#xB098;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xB9C8;&#xCC2C;&#xAC00;&#xC9C0;&#xB2E4;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">. </span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC989;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">, </span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic;text-decoration:underline\">&#xCD08;&#xAE30;&#xD654;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic;text-decoration:underline\"> </span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic;text-decoration:underline\">&#xD560;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic;text-decoration:underline\"> state</span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic;text-decoration:underline\">&#xAC12;</span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC774;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC778;&#xC790;&#xB85C;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xB4E4;&#xC5B4;&#xAC00;&#xAC8C;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xB41C;&#xB2E4;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">.</span></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<h2 style=\"font-size:14pt;color:#2e75b5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">useState<span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xB294;</span> <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/Destructuring_assignment#Array_destructuring\">Array destructuring</a><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xBC29;&#xC2DD;&#xC744;</span> <span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xCC44;&#xD0DD;&#xD55C;&#xB2E4;</span>. </h2>\n\t\t\t<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><a href=\"https://reactjs.org/docs/hooks-state.html#tip-what-do-square-brackets-mean\">Reactjs.org- Tip: What Do Square Brackets Mean?</a></p>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xBCC0;&#xC218;&#xBA85;&#xC744;</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC0AC;&#xC6A9;&#xC790;</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xB9C8;&#xC74C;&#xB300;&#xB85C;</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC9C0;&#xC815;&#xD560;</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC218;</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC788;&#xAC8C;</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xD558;&#xAE30;</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC704;&#xD568;&#xC774;&#xB77C;&#xACE0;</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xD55C;&#xB2E4;</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">.</span></p>\n\t\t\t<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">Destructuring</span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xD558;&#xC9C0;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC54A;&#xB294;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC2A4;&#xD0C0;&#xC77C;&#xB85C;&#xB294;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC544;&#xB798;&#xC758;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xCF54;&#xB4DC;&#xC640;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> </span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xAC19;&#xB2E4;</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">.</span></p>\n\t\t\t<table style=\"border:1px solid;border-collapse:collapse\">\n\t\t\t\t<tbody><tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color:black;border:1px solid\"><span lang=\"ko-KR\"><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding\">  </span><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding;color:#ae91ae\">var </span><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding;color:white\">fruitStateVariable </span><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding;color:#9398a0\">= </span><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding;color:#6ca3d9\">useState</span><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding;color:#70a39c\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding;color:#73a376\">&apos;banana&apos;</span><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding;color:#70a39c\">); </span><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding;color:#979797\">// Returns a pair</span><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding\">&#xFFFC;</span><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding\">  </span><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding;color:#ae91ae\">var </span><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding;color:white\">fruit </span><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding;color:#9398a0\">= </span><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding;color:white\">fruitStateVariable</span><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding;color:#70a39c\">[</span><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding;color:#5a9bcf\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding;color:#70a39c\">]; </span><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding;color:#979797\">// First item in a pair</span><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding\">&#xFFFC;</span><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding\">  </span><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding;color:#ae91ae\">var </span><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding;color:white\">setFruit </span><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding;color:#9398a0\">= </span><span style=\"font-family:D2Coding;color:white\">fruitStateVariable</span